text: Secrets of Sulphur Springs is an American time-travel mystery thriller drama television series. it aired on Disney Channel from January 15, 2021 to May 5, 2023. It was created by writer Tracey Thomson, who also serves as an executive producer alongside Charles Pratt Jr. It is set in the fictional Louisiana town of Sulphur Springs. In January 2024, it was canceled after three seasons. Category:Television series by Disney Category:English-language television programs Category:2023 American television series endings
